{"bio":null,"bio_l":"没有人见过主宰尤涅若面具下的真面目。甚至有人认为他没有脸部。作为公然反抗腐败领主的惩罚，主宰被古老的遮面之岛流放了，这反而救了他的性命。他的岛屿在一个充斥着复仇魔法的夜晚被海浪彻底毁灭了。他成了岛屿上古老主宰传统中礼仪和剑术的唯一传承者。作为这项传统最后的开拓者，尤涅若的自信和勇气来自他坚持不懈的锻炼，他独创的剑术证明他从未停止挑战自我。一如既往的，他的内心和他的表情一样难以理解。对于一位曾两度失去一切的英雄，主宰永远不知疲倦的战斗着，他相信，胜利必将到来。","stats":"<img src=\"Int\" alt=\"Intelligence\" />Intelligence:14 + 1.40<br /><img src=\"Agi\" alt=\"Agility\" />Agility:26 + 2.40<br /><img src=\"Str\" alt=\"Strength\" />Strength:20 + 1.90<br /><img src=\"Attack\" alt=\"Damage\" />Damage:24 - 28<br /><img src=\"Speed\" alt=\"Movespeed\" />Movespeed:305<br /><img src=\"Defense\" alt=\"Armor\" />Armor:3.64","stats1":[["Int","Intelligence","14 + 1.40"],["Agi","Agility","26 + 2.40"],["Str","Strength","20 + 1.90"],["Attack","Damage","24 - 28"],["Speed","Movespeed","305"],["Defense","Armor","3.64"]],"detailstats":"<div class=\"redboxContent\"><div class=\"redboxTop\"></div><div id=\"statsInner\"><div id=\"statsLeft\"><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol\">25</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">15</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">1</div>等级</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,776</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,035</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">530</div>生命值</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">879</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">437</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">182</div>魔法值</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">128-132</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">84-88</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">50-54</div>攻击力</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">15</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">8</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">4</div>护甲</div></div><div id=\"statsRight\"><div class=\"statRow\"></div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">1800 / 800</div>视野范围</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">128</div>攻击范围</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">N/A</div>弹道速度</div></div><br clear=\"both\" /></div><div class=\"redboxBottom\"></div></div>","detailstats1":[["生命值","1,776","1,035","530"],["魔法值","879","437","182"],["攻击力","128-132","84-88","50-54"],["护甲","15","8","4"]],"detailstats2":[["视野范围","1800 / 800"],["攻击范围","128"],["弹道速度","N/A"]],"abilities":[{"key_name":"juggernaut_blade_fury","dname":"剑刃风暴","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">无目标</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\">魔法</span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\">否</span>","desc":"舞起具有破坏性力量的剑刃风暴，对主宰周围的敌方单位造成伤害，并使主宰对魔法免疫。持续5秒。","dmg":"攻击力:<span class=\"attribVal\">80 / 105 / 130 / 155</span>","notes":"此技能对机械单位无效。<br />在剑刃风暴期间可以使用物品。<br />主宰在施放剑刃风暴的过程中依然可以进行物理攻击。但是只有不受剑刃风暴伤害的单位，如守卫和建筑才会受到这些物理伤害。<br />按等级总共造成400/525/650/775点伤害。","attrib":"作用范围： <span class=\"attribVal\">250</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:120/110/100/90<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:42/34/26/18","lore":"无论是战士还是法师，都害怕尤涅若的武士刀剑技。","hurl":"Juggernaut"},{"key_name":"juggernaut_healing_ward","dname":"治疗守卫","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">点目标</span>","desc":"召唤一个治疗守卫，按周围友军单位最大生命值的一定比例治疗他们。治疗守卫可以移动，移动速度为420。持续25秒。","dmg":"","notes":"可以控制治疗守卫。<br />多个治疗守卫的效果不会叠加。","attrib":"每秒最大生命值回复： <span class=\"attribVal\">2% / 3% / 4% / 5%</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:120/125/130/135<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:60","lore":"这是主宰在遮面之岛学到的一项惯用技巧，战斗证明会使用一点巫毒魔法治疗伤口是很有效的。","hurl":"Juggernaut"},{"key_name":"juggernaut_blade_dance","dname":"剑舞","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">被动</span>","desc":"主宰有一定概率在攻击时造成双倍伤害。","dmg":"","notes":"","attrib":"致命一击伤害： <span class=\"attribVal\">200%</span><br />\n致命一击概率： <span class=\"attribVal\">20% / 25% / 30% / 35%</span>","cmb":"","lore":"作为他对剑技传承的最后承诺，尤涅若立誓将使此剑技为世人所铭记。","hurl":"Juggernaut"},{"key_name":"juggernaut_omni_slash","dname":"无敌斩","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">单位目标</span><br />影响：<span class=\"attribVal\">敌方单位</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\"><font color=\"#71a9ea\">物理</font></span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\"><font color=\"#70EA72\">是</font></span>","desc":"主宰挥剑跃向敌人，随后再斩击附近的其它敌方单位，每次斩击造成200-225点伤害。主宰在无敌斩期间无敌。\r\n\r\n可用神杖升级。","dmg":"","notes":"无敌斩期间可以使用物品。<br />可以对技能免疫单位施放。<br />每次斩击的间隔是0.4秒。<br />小兵和中立生物只须一次斩击就被秒杀。","attrib":"斩击次数： <span class=\"attribVal\">3 / 6 / 9</span><br />\n斩击跳跃范围： <span class=\"attribVal\">425</span><br />\n<span class=\"scepterVal\"><font color=\"#6fe771\">神杖升级斩击次数：</font></span> <span class=\"attribVal\">6 / 9 / 12</span><br />\n<span class=\"scepterVal\"><font color=\"#6fe771\">神杖升级冷却时间：</font></span> <span class=\"attribVal\">70</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:200/275/350<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:130/120/110","lore":"“自律与勤练带来力量。”","hurl":"Juggernaut"}],"itembuilds":{"Starting":["tango","flask","clarity","branches","slippers","slippers"],"Early":["boots","poor_mans_shield","magic_stick","bracer"],"Core":["phase_boots","magic_wand","ancient_janggo","ultimate_scepter","tpscroll"],"Luxury":["sange_and_yasha","butterfly","desolator","bfury","vladmir","black_king_bar"]},"skillup":[{"groupName":"常规技能加点方式","desc":"<p>比较科学的加点方式，前期多一级黄点让你不会很容易出现差一点儿魔放不了大招，早点儿点起棒子可以让团队在团战完了能迅速恢复推塔，不需要很高的等级，两级足够。</p>","abilityKeys":["juggernaut_blade_fury","attribute_bonus","juggernaut_blade_fury","juggernaut_healing_ward","juggernaut_blade_fury","juggernaut_omni_slash","juggernaut_blade_fury","juggernaut_healing_ward","juggernaut_blade_dance","juggernaut_blade_dance","juggernaut_blade_dance","juggernaut_omni_slash","juggernaut_blade_dance","juggernaut_healing_ward","juggernaut_healing_ward","juggernaut_omni_slash","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus"]},{"groupName":"黄点疯脸","desc":"疯脸流剑圣：因为剑圣暴击的概率很高，有时候平A要比剑刃风暴伤害来的高，所以放弃了主剑刃风暴的加点只加一级用来逃生和前几级来打伤害。平砍则是需要高属性来支撑，剑圣暴击升级只是增加概率不增加倍数，通过点黄点再前期让剑圣增加三围要比点技能效果好得多。","abilityKeys":["juggernaut_blade_fury","juggernaut_healing_ward","juggernaut_blade_dance","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","juggernaut_omni_slash",